always kabhi kabhi ( meaning ' always sometimes ' ) is a 2011 hindi romance film directed by roshan abbas , and produced by shahrukh khan under red chillies entertainment .   it introduced ali fazal , giselli monteiro , zoa morani , satyajeet dubey withsatish shah , lilette dubey , vijay raaz , mukesh tiwari and manoj joshi playing supporting roles .   the film released on 17 june 2011 .   it focuses on four teenagers embarking on a dramatic journey during their incident-packed final year at school .